fehd.ADR_EN: G/F (REAR PORTION), 102 AP LEI CHAU MAIN STREET, AP LEI CHAU, HONG KONG
fehd.ADR_TC: 香港鴨脷洲鴨脷洲大街102號地下(後部份)

reviews.text: Good and authentic. Goose and seafood. Goose offals is exceptional!

quite disappointed and underwhelmed with 澄海小馆actually 

we went ap lei chai 鸭脷洲 this afternoon and took ferry HK$2.50pax to aberdeen pier and free feery to visit jumbo..

so plan 3pax dinner at 澄海小馆...

of course we not expecting service or help with menu..basically you have to already know what to order at these eating places..

we ordered the 狮头鹅例牌HK$148..its a small serving with lots of nuts and tofu to prop up..fortunately taste of the lor (卤）was good..this is expensive c/w 九记打冷which bigger serving for HK$88

likewise the 小炒皇HK$98 was flavourful had some wokhae but also not as good c/w 九记打冷

the big intestine amd goose liver at HK$30 per item quite ok..

overall HK$317 for 3pax ok not so cheap as we ordered only 3 dishes

27.5.2019
Food quality is good, value for money. If you are visitor, you must try some local food here.
A nice chiu chow restaurant serving the neighborhood
The Shredded Chicken is quite good
